casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Francis Joseph COYLE, Jr.
No. D-2991.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 19, 2017.
Francis Joseph Coyle, Jr., of Rock Island, Illinois, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
